{
  "stem": "14897.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was not even time to hide, because the bang on the door immediately.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember we were on the third floor, but this was a young Ukrainian soldier and he ran up as soon as he saw her and pushed in the door.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he found us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she was-- she was a good-looking young woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she started to beg him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She says, I am so young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't want to die yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Save me, please, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he said, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And not only did he not take us, but he stood in the hall on that stairway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when the other soldiers came, he said, don't bother going in this apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was there already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There's nobody there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were saved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we could see-- you know, we went to the window and we looked through the-- the curtains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we could see them rounding up other people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this same young man dragged an old man with a beard out of an apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the man was resisting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he kicked him to death right in the yard, the same man who saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- Why do you think he did that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what I-- what I learned from that is [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when you have the-- the power over the life or deaths of other people, it is both brutalizing and makes you very capricious.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you could see events like this over and over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The same person who would save one person's life and kill another person.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It gives you that sense of power that you can do whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, if you're going to kill everybody, then you don't have the sense of power.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
